Thank you for your question. Your `/upload` route isn't working because you need to create a third route, an `app.get('/upload',....)` route that will render a pug file. This upload page should have a simple HTML Form on it. Please let me know if you have any other questions.
Hello everyone. If you're having issues with this, please ensure your account has Marketing Hub Enterprise, which gives you access to custom objects.
